data.description: AMAZING LOCATION, two-story end unit garage town-home within minutes of I-85, I-40, well established neighborhood, short distance to Duke University, shopping, dining, parks. Colonial traditional floor plan, open kitchen with dining, ample cabinets, leading to patio. Family room features a wood-burning fireplace. Owner’s suite features a WIC & private bath, plus two additional bedrooms, dining room, open to landscaped common grounds.
